{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"375-playtime","title":"Playtime","description":"Golu and Chhotu sure make a funny pair. Read about their antics in this funny story.","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Manisha Chaudhry"],"illustrators":["Ajit Narayan"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/375-playtime"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/721916/size3/906e74898bf061f7abefb75c6319ad63.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/721916/size6/906e74898bf061f7abefb75c6319ad63.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/4632/size6/05d348a35d69e770f33ebc1923eac981.jpg","text":"The little elephant's name was Golu. He was as round as a drum. The little rabbit was called Chhotu. He looked like a ball of cotton.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/4633/size6/3939910b7a0579d539764e852c1da78b.jpg","text":"They played together.\nOne day, Golu said, “Let’s play a new game today.”","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/4634/size6/7cf442bcab4b8b77a04b8952acf05833.jpg","text":"“You sit down. I’ll land on your back in one flying leap,” said Chhotu. Golu sat down. Chhotu took a mighty leap.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/4635/size6/47c421dba71f4326098256871213ae8d.jpg","text":"Thump! He landed on Golu’s back.\n“Wow!” laughed Golu and said, “My turn now. You sit down and I will leap on your back.”","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/4636/size6/2a1ed1000db583e991e99cdd5b6d1e08.jpg","text":"“You!”\n“Yes, me.”\n“How can you do that?” asked Chhotu.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/4637/size6/58232a7004c248f5ea5ce5d2fdb4ab28.jpg","text":"\"Like this!\" Golu showed him.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/4638/size6/4a2f2a72d8ad701133b1e8e23c65674b.jpg","text":"Thud… thud… thud…\nA shower of coconuts came down on Golu’s head.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/4639/size6/0315705cc8174fcbb44d7512317be519.jpg","text":"He ran away on fat legs, scared.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/4640/size6/d3c51de81ea2d4bf598492a3441f597b.jpg","text":"One small coconut fell on Chhotu.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/4641/size6/30988ba27514499635a972b370aead1f.jpg","text":"‘That’s better,’ thought Chhotu, ‘Better a coconut than an elephant on my head!’","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":10,"words":138}}